Licencing Information for OLA
=========================================

C++
-----------------------------------------
The files required for libola and libolacommon are licenced under the LGPLv2.1
(or later), this means you are free to link against the OLA client library in
your own programs.

The files required for libolaserver and olad are licenced under the GPL v2 (or
later).

Python
------------------------------------------
The Python client API is LGPL, the examples and RDM Responder Test Suite is
GPL.

Simon Newton
15/7/2005
